OL,7,FThe course is one of the most popular
OL,8,Fon the Welsh running calendar, partly
OL,9,Fdown to its flat terrain leading it to
OL,10,Fbeing named among the fastest
OL,11,Fmarathons in the world.
OL,13,FRunners will have their times amended
OL,14,Fautomatically if they are applying for
OL,15,Fa 'Good For Age' entry into the London
OL,16,FMarathon.
