OL,3,CNewport Marathon organisers issue
OL,4,Capology after course distance was too
OL,5,Clong
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, the AUKCM has
OL,8,Fconcluded that there was an error with
OL,9,Ftheir course measurement, resulting in
OL,10,Fthe marathon being 276m too long,
OL,11,Fwhich equates to 0.171 miles.
OL,13,F"Run 4 Wales is disappointed that this
OL,14,Fhas happened at one of its events and
OL,15,Funderstands and apologises
OL,16,Funreservedly to those impacted,
OL,17,Fparticularly those aiming for good for
OL,18,Fage qualifying times.
