OL,4,Capology after course distance was too
OL,5,Clong
OL,7,F"For this reason, we have been working
OL,8,Fwith London Marathon Events who have
OL,9,Fagreed that times will be amended for
OL,10,Fthose applying for a Good for Age
OL,11,Fentry at the TCS London Marathon,
OL,12,Fshould the athlete have been affected
OL,13,Fin gaining a place.
OL,15,F"An equivalent number of seconds will
OL,16,Fbe removed from the finish times of
OL,17,Fthose applying for a Good for Age
OL,18,Fentry.
