OL,4,Capology after course distance was too
OL,5,Clong
OL,7,F"For example, a three-hour finish time
OL,8,Fwould be corrected approximately by 70
OL,9,Fseconds, a 3.5-hour finish time would
OL,10,Fbe corrected by 82 seconds and a four-
OL,11,Fhour finish time would be corrected by
OL,12,F94 seconds. This will be done
OL,13,Fautomatically via the London Marathon
OL,14,Fsystem when applying.
OL,16,F"The AUKCM can confirm there were no
OL,17,Fissues with their half marathon or 10K
OL,18,Fcourse measurements."
